n: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"></span><p /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">A "Mail Drop" location is an address where a business or service accepts mail deliveries on behalf of a customer. ECoptical.com will deliver to Mail Drop locations such as a UPS Store (formerly Mail Boxes Etc.). However, ECoptical.com is unable to deliver to Post Office Boxes or APO/FPO addresses, which are military overseas mail drops. <br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /></span></p><p /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">Our primary carrier is <strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">FedEx</span></strong>. We also ship by <strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">DHL, TNT, UPS</span></strong> Express or <strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">HKEMS</span></strong> to worldwide.<br /></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"><br /></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">We can also provide the tracking information for items valued over US$20 so that you can feel confident and comfortable with your purchase. Package usually ships within 24-48 hours of payment being received (Weekends 48 hrs). </span></p><p /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"></span><p /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">Please note that although we will ship out your item within 48 hours, your item may leave <place w:st="on" />Hong Kong</place /> after 2-4 days due to Post Office processing time. So please add transit time and handling time to have realistic delivery time. </span></p><p /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"><br /><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">About the delivery time: </b></span></p><p /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"><br /><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">FedEx</span></strong>: it will take 1-3 days (weekends and holidays excepted) for delivery. For <country-region w:st="on" />Spain</country-region />, <country-region w:st="on" />Italy</country-region />, <place w:st="on" /><country-region w:st="on" />Brazil</country-region /></place /> and some other countries, items will take longer time to arrive due to customs clearance period. </span></p><p /><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><br /><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Please note</b> that delays caused by carriers we cannot be held responsible for. Shipping time is only estimated and not guaranteed.</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left" /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left" /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="left" /><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso